Gene to Symbol Mappings

Gene to Symbol Mappings

# S4 method for bcbioSingleCell
gene2symbol(object)

# S4 method for seurat
gene2symbol(object)

Arguments

object

Object.

Examples

load(system.file("extdata/bcb.rda", package = "bcbioSingleCell"))
load(system.file("extdata/seurat.rda", package = "bcbioSingleCell"))

# bcbioRNASeq
gene2symbol(bcb) %>% glimpse()
#> Observations: 64,661
#> Variables: 2
#> $ ensgene <chr> "ENSG00000000003", "ENSG00000000005", "ENSG00000000419", "E...
#> $ symbol  <chr> "TSPAN6", "TNMD", "DPM1", "SCYL3", "C1orf112", "FGR", "CFH"...

# seurat
gene2symbol(seurat) %>% glimpse()
#> Observations: 64,661
#> Variables: 2
#> $ ensgene <chr> "ENSG00000000003", "ENSG00000000005", "ENSG00000000419", "E...
#> $ symbol  <chr> "TSPAN6", "TNMD", "DPM1", "SCYL3", "C1orf112", "FGR", "CFH"...
